    {"id":"TEAM-GITHUB-001","area":"team","title":"Expose Create GitHub Development Issue from Annotation through editor, both tree surfaces and Command Palette without storing a manual PAT","status":"done","note":"Repository/source/menu tests and Extension Host registration coverage confirm activation and the 86-command manifest. The issue line and post-network trace mutation use the canonical store; no real GitHub request runs in tests."},
