    {"id":"QA-MENU-001","area":"quality","title":"Validate activation-time registration and guided no-target behavior for every public command, not only manifest discoverability","status":"in_progress","note":"The read-only audit found all 86 declared commands registered exactly once and reachable from native menus, plus the exact ten-command internal allow-list. The CommentReply/Delete mismatch is fixed under BUG-COMMENTS-002; public handler walkthrough coverage and the empty-window Move lifecycle contract remain pending."},
